{"tid":1085880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真心 香港有得收支那宝都幾好","createTime":"2019-03-31T13:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T13:30:04.000Z","uid":25071,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f0d5ae066dc6029627903ccdc9679402ce013783","tid":1085880,"uid":25071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:19:48.000Z","msg":"俾小小背景大家先 我有份兼職係連鎖雪糕舖到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始公司話可以收支那宝我真係幾失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前啲蝗話俾支那宝 微信 一句就大聲ban埋去話無不知幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係過咗一兩個星期 真心好感謝公司有依個決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有支那宝真係有好有唔好<br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) 收錢真係快左十倍 啲蝗真係唔撚帶現金去旅行 碌親銀聯又慢又要密碼又要簽名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一無得收支那宝就要打去唔撚知係商場邊層既三姑六婆過黎俾錢 等到雪鳩都溶糕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 收錢用QR CODE 唔撚再掂到支那佬啲唔剪指甲既污joe手 班仆街成日一路排隊揀雪糕 就一路用啲武則天咁長既尾甲了鼻屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次比雪糕或都收親九成九會掂到佢地 佢地無意識避開身體接觸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1) 好多講純正廣東話 好眉好貌既香港人用支那宝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地收得支那寶就會有啲QR CODE係當眼位置比蝗拎優惠 平幾蚊 但貪少便宜既香港人竟然為左幾蚊用支那宝 真係好撚好撚失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2) 用支那宝啲香港人正一屎忽鬼 又要做雞 又要貞節牌坊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十個有九個都係話比 AH LEE PAY 以為講句雞腸就高級過啲蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明個腦已經比強國侵蝕左 有咁多淪陷左既香港人我真係公司收左支那寶我先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77e8ef4ae77257ecff91f0c773587803eac4cb2","tid":1085880,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"負面宣傳有用？"},{"pid":"7114ba480d1116e83ac6e888325accd1d21315de","tid":1085880,"uid":25071,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c77e8ef4ae77257ecff91f0c773587803eac4cb2","tid":1085880,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:20:47.000Z","msg":"負面宣傳有用？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:22:01.000Z","msg":"支持蝗用 反對香港人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8eb8f4be8771425d031e488178695bc6dcddb7","tid":1085880,"uid":25071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67deff10fef0d740be7f6fe5f6313aa292fc7b7a","tid":1085880,"uid":25071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"無收銀既同路人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e1ae27bf9138fef18301b66c4f81d808dbc49b","tid":1085880,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T13:30:04.000Z","msg":"下次佢地講alipay<br />\n<br />\n你就話 哦 支付寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}